name: Glimmerpaw the Majestic Mouse

extensions.description: Glimmerpaw is the majestic mouse of the Solana blockchain. More than just a memecoin, Glimmerpaw combines NFT charm with meme culture and community magic. From fairy tale forests to moonlit rallies, Glimmerpaw is your next favorite mouse token.
